Ask HN: Startup banking recommendations (good app/online experience)?
text: I was searching on reddit and pretty much 100% of the threads are recommending a credit union. I think it is hit or miss. Plenty of credit unions have terrible online experience. In light of SVB failures and what not, what's HN's recommendation for an amazing online bank that offers checking/savings accounts for businesses? We're talking about less than $1M in cash. Where do you bank with your startup/LLC?

Ask HN: How does your team answer “What's shipping?”
text:
How clear are exec teams and product leads at your company about what is shipping and when? If they know, how do they know? Project management tools don't give you a clear sense of what's shipping and when.

How often do you have to answer questions of the nature "hey, when is that thing shipping?", "what's shipping in this next release?" etc.

Ask HN: Anyone Using PlanetScale in Production?
text:
Hi We are considering switching to Planetscale for our multi tenant SAAS (separate db per tenant). The serverless side of things (where we don't have to worry about allocating specific CPU/RAM/Storage) is appealing.

I would love to hear from anyone who is using planetscale in production and if you would recommend based on the product and their support ?
